yle="color:#068481">JavaScript test integration</strong>\r\nRun your tests faster, <a href="http://trac.getwindmill.com/wiki/BookChapter-4-3-JavascriptTests">write them in JavaScript</a>! Also provides the complete set of JSUnit functions.\r\n\r\n<strong style="color:#068481">Windmill Controller</strong>\r\nClick, type, sleep, assert, pretty much anything you can think of doing to your web page is available as a windmill controller method.', 'Meet Windmill', 0, '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '447-revision-40', '', '', '2009-03-31 03:13:47', '2009-03-31 07:13:47', '', 447, 'http://www.getwindmill.com/archives/487', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
